com.github.gwtbootstrap.client.ui

Class Collapse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.gwtbootstrap.client.ui.base.MarkupWidget
      • com.github.gwtbootstrap.client.ui.Collapse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasId, HasVisibility, HasVisibleHandlers, AcceptsOneWidget, HasOneWidget, HasWidgets, IsWidget, Iterable<Widget>

    public class Collapse
extends MarkupWidget
implements HasVisibility, HasVisibleHandlers
    Markup widget of Collapse

    It's a markup widget (decorator widget). it's can exchange child to Collapsible widget. It's need trigger, You have 2 ways to create trigger.

    1. Using CollapseTrigger.
    2. Calling toggle().

    UiBinder Usage:

     <b:Collapse b:id="toggle1" defaultOpen="true">
   <!-- it can be added any widget, but accept one wdiget.
   <b:Label>aaa</b:Label>
 </b:Collapse>
    Since:
    2.2.1.0
    Author:
    ohashi keisuke
    See Also:
    Accordion, Collapse, CollapseTrigger, Twitter Bootstrap document
